imdb.plot outline: Two Half-Opposing Sisters Which Had The Hereditary Power Of Witchcraft Will Be Divided By A Prophecy That Can Cause Them To Cause A War On Their Own One Will Bring Cure And Healing And The Other One Curse And Destruction,Now The Powers Of Light And Darkness Are At Work They Struggle For Love,Their Own Rights,And Even Their Sisterhood.Will The Prophecy Behind The Great Controversy Between Angela And Lucille Can Be Finally Fulfilled?
imdb.title: Haplos
plot: Two Half-Opposing Sisters Which Had The Hereditary Power Of Witchcraft Will Be Divided By A Prophecy That Can Cause Them To Cause A War On Their Own One Will Bring Cure And Healing And The Other One Curse And Destruction,Now The Powers Of Light And Darkness Are At Work They Struggle For Love,Their Own Rights,And Even Their Sisterhood.Will The Prophecy Behind The Great Controversy Between Angela And Lucille Can Be Finally Fulfilled?::John Joshua Fernandez
